                              <H3>A Simple CAPTCHA Image Verification in C# and 
                              ASP.Net</H3>
                              <P class=MsoNormal 
                              style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></P>
                              <P class=MsoNormal 
                              style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">Websites(hosted in 
                              internet domains)&nbsp;&nbsp;that offer users to 
                              post contents will have a greater threat from 
                              spammers and automated programs that can submit 
                              spam contents. So, it is vital to have a mechanism 
                              to verify the users if they are really humans who 
                              are posting the contents.</P>
                              <P class=MsoNormal 
                              style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></P>
                              <P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">The 
                              following little article will help fighting this 
                              threat using a simple CAPTCHA image verification 
                              developed using HttpHandler and Session variable. 
                              </P>
                              <P class=MsoNormal 
                              style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></P>
                              <P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">To 
                              develop this,</P>
                              <P class=MsoNormal 
                              style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></P>
                              <P class=MsoNormal 
                              style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">Include a Generic 
                              HttpHandler that can render the content of a 
                              Session variable as an image. Refer the below code 
                              snippet that generates an image from Session 
                              variable.</P>
                              <P class=MsoNormal 
                              style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></P>
                              <P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><B 
                              style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">Captcha.ashx<o:p></o:p></B></P>
                              <P class=MsoNormal 
                              style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT 
                              color=#a52a2a>&lt;%@ WebHandler Language="C#" 
                              Class="Captcha" %&gt;</FONT></P>
                              <P class=MsoNormal 
                              style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT 
                              color=#a52a2a>using System;</FONT></P>
                              <P class=MsoNormal 
                              style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT 
                              color=#a52a2a>using System.Web;</FONT></P>
                              <P class=MsoNormal 
                              style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT 
                              color=#a52a2a>using System.Drawing;</FONT></P>
                              <P class=MsoNormal 
                              style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT 
                              color=#a52a2a>using System.IO;</FONT></P>
                              <P class=MsoNormal 
                              style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT 
                              color=#a52a2a>using 
                              System.Web.SessionState;</FONT></P>
                              <P class=MsoNormal 
                              style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><o:p><FONT 
                              color=#a52a2a>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></P>
                              <P class=MsoNormal 
                              style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT 
                              color=#a52a2a>public class Captcha : IHttpHandler, 
                              IReadOnlySessionState</FONT></P>
                              <P class=MsoNormal 
                              style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><FONT 
